+//! PDE-Based Attention
+//!
+//! Continuous-time attention using partial differential equations.
+//!
+//! ## Key Concepts
+//!
+//! 1. **Diffusion Smoothing**: Heat equation on attention graph
+//! 2. **Graph Laplacian**: L = D - W for key similarity
