+//! └─────────┘       └───────────┘       └───────────┘
+//! Plan safe         Certify policy      Measure
+//! routing paths     constraints         distributional
+//!                                       distances
+//! ```
+//!
+//! ## Quick Start
+//!
+//! ```rust
